<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天不愧是复活节，<delay20 />
这还真是一片盛况。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过过节嘛，<delay8 />就是要热热闹闹才行。<delay frames="40" />
别看我这样，<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也在好好享受哦？<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然可能跟平时差不多就是了。<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00">因为今天是复活节，<delay20 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以<colour id="3" />蹦蹦<colour id="65535" />来广场上了对吧？<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />听说他事先<delay8 />把彩蛋啊、还有手册之类的东西<delay8 />
都藏在<delay8 />岛上各处了。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那家伙还真是勤恳认真啊。<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你怎么还<delay8 />待在我家里，<delay20 />
不赶紧去收集彩蛋吗？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一直这样磨磨蹭蹭，可就要被其他人拿走咯。<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />话虽如此，<delay20 />在岛上四处奔走收集彩蛋，
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好像还挺费劲的啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是彩蛋能自己送上门来，<delay8 />
那就再好不过了，<delay20 /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊哈哈哈！</message>
	<message label="100" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />复活节近在眼前了啊。<delay frames="40" />
岛上到处都是彩蛋的节日<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />说起来，<delay8 /><colour id="3" />陆德里<colour id="65535" />之前好像说过。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />他参加<delay8 />里数旅行时，
在旅行的目的地，<delay20 />
看到岛上的岩石旁边掉了很多彩蛋。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然我觉得应该是那家伙<delay8 />肚子太饿，
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />把石头错看成了蛋就是了。<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你要是感兴趣的话，就去看看吧。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />复活节近在眼前了啊。<delay frames="40" />
岛上到处都是彩蛋的节日<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />说起来，<delay8 />我小时候好像听过这么一个故事。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />据说<delay8 />这个世界上，<delay8 />
生长着一种奇特的椰子树，<delay8 />
只要敲打它就会掉出彩蛋来。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果这座<tag a="110" b="32" />有椰子树的话，<delay8 />
说不定可以试试看啊。<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />毕竟凡事都说不准嘛。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">对了，<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="3" />，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你知道今年的复活节<delay20 />
是<delay20 /><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="90" b="35" arg="0xcd00" />月<tag a="90" b="36" arg="0xcd00" />日吗？<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你可要记牢咯，<delay frames="40" />
因为复活节<delay8 />可是能够
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />尽情吃蛋的重要节日啊！<pageBreak /><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><size value="75" />什么，<delay8 />你说不是<tag a="110" b="0" />？<delay frames="60" /><size value="100" />
<anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />总、<delay8 />总之是个喜庆的节日就对了！<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那种小事就别在意啦！<delay frames="40" /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />啊哈哈哈！</message>
